  "2026-07-16T16:58:08.386Z",codex-root,Confirmed in Actions runs 26767553085 and 26744281604.
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:58:08.386Z",codex-root,Switch .github/dependabot.yml from npm to bun; do not add package-lock.json to a Bun-owned repository.
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T16:58:08.386Z",codex-root,"Dependabot Bun support requires the modern text bun.lock, which this repo already uses."
