close_reason: Native Bun dependency automation delivered in PR #45
body: "Every open npm Dependabot PR fails Validate (Bun) at bun install --frozen-lockfile because bun.lock is left stale. GitHub now officially supports package-ecosystem bun for text bun.lock files, so the repository should use its declared package manager end to end."
